## Visual Compliance Agent

The Visual Compliance Agent automates OCA compliance validation using a **Skills Registry** architecture:

### Compliance Checks

- **Manifest compliance** - Odoo 18.0 version format, LGPL-3 license, InsightPulseAI metadata
- **Directory structure** - Single canonical `odoo_addons/` directory
- **Module naming** - Standardized `ipai_*` prefix for custom modules
- **Documentation** - README.rst files for all modules

### Skills Registry Architecture

The Visual Compliance Agent uses a modular, pluggable architecture:

- **Skills** (`agents/skills.yaml`) - Atomic capabilities with standard interface
- **Skill Registry** (`agents/skill_registry.py`) - Dynamic skill loader
- **CLI Wrapper** (`agents/run_skill.py`) - Command-line skill executor
- **Validators** - Skill wrappers around core validation tools

See [agents/visual-compliance/](https://github.com/jgtolentino/insightpulse-odoo/tree/main/agents/visual-compliance) for implementation details.

### Usage

```bash
# Run single skill
python -m agents.run_skill odoo.manifest.validate --repo-path .

# Run skill with auto-fix
python -m agents.run_skill odoo.manifest.validate --repo-path . --fix

# Run skill profile (multiple skills)
python -m agents.run_skill --profile fast_check --repo-path .

# List available skills
python -m agents.run_skill --list

# Full compliance scan
python -m agents.run_skill visual_compliance.full_scan --repo-path . --json
```

### Available Skills

- `odoo.manifest.validate` - Manifest compliance validation and auto-fix
- `odoo.directory.validate` - Directory structure validation and consolidation
- `odoo.naming.validate` - Module naming convention validation
- `odoo.readme.validate` - README.rst generation and validation
- `visual_compliance.full_scan` - Complete compliance scan with reporting

### Skill Profiles

- `fast_check` - Quick manifest + directory validation for CI
- `full_compliance` - Complete validation suite
- `pr_review` - Validation for PR checks (no auto-fix)
- `weekly_audit` - Full scan with issue creation

